rf_mod <-
  rand_forest(trees = 1000) %>% 
  set_engine("ranger") %>% 
  set_mode("regression")
set.seed(234)
rf_fit <-
  rf_mod %>% 
  fit(Fatigue ~ ., data = df1)

folds <- vfold_cv(df1, v = 10)
folds
#  10-fold cross-validation 
rf_wf <-
  workflow() %>% 
  add_model(rf_mod) %>% 
  add_formula(Fatigue ~ .)

set.seed(456)
rf_fit_rs <-
  rf_wf %>% 
  fit_resamples(folds)
collect_metrics(rf_fit_rs)
compositions <-
  df1 %>% 
  select(C, Si, Mn, P, S, Ni, Cr, Cu, Mo)
compositions %>% 
  distinct()
clusters <- tibble(n = 2:nrow(distinct(compositions)))
clusters
clusters <-
  clusters %>% 
  mutate(k = map(n, function(n) { kmeans(compositions, centers = n) }))
clusters
clusters %>% 
  mutate(ss = map_dbl(k, ~.x$tot.withinss)) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(n, ss)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_line() +
  scale_x_continuous(limits = c(0, 50))

df2 <-
  df1 %>% 
  group_by(NT, THT, THt, THQCr, CT, Ct, DT, Dt, QmT, TT, Tt, TCr) %>% 
  nest() %>% 
  rowid_to_column(var = "process") %>% 
  mutate(ndata = map_int(data, nrow)) %>% 
  relocate(process, ndata) %>% 
  unnest(cols = c(data)) %>% 
  ungroup()
df2 %>% 
  filter(process == 1) %>% 
  select(C:Mo) %>% 
  trunc_mat(n = 100)
